<h2>Subscribe to our mailing list</h2>

<p>Subscribe to receive EMOM event announcements and related updates.</p>
<p>We'll email you a confirmation link. Your subscription is only activated after you open that link.</p>

<form id="newsletter-subscribe-form">
  <label for="newsletter-email">Email</label>
  <input type="email" id="newsletter-email" name="email" required>

  <label for="newsletter-first-name">First name (optional)</label>
  <input type="text" id="newsletter-first-name" name="first_name">

  <label for="newsletter-last-name">Last name (optional)</label>
  <input type="text" id="newsletter-last-name" name="last_name">

  <button type="submit">Send confirmation link</button>
</form>

<p id="newsletter-subscribe-status" aria-live="polite"></p>

<script src="/assets/scripts/newsletter_subscribe.js"></script>
